FBPAD
=====

Fbpad is a small and simple linux framebuffer virtual terminal.
It manages many terminals through tags; each tag can have at most two
terminals.  Tags are represented with a single letter.

==============  =======================================
key		command
==============  =======================================
m-c		execute a shell
m-m		execute mail program
m-e		execute editor program
m-x 		switch to tag 'x'
m-j		switch to alt terminal in this tag
m-k		like m-j
m-p		show tag summary
m-o		jump to last tag
m-tab		show next terminal
c-m-q		quit fbpad
==============  =======================================

INSTALLATION
============

Change config.h file to customize the settings.  Then run make.
